 ans et sa mère, Isold Hawberke, avait 28 ans. Elle a épousé Walter Hopton en 1361, à Hopton, Suffolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Ils ont eu au moins 2 fils. Elle est décédée le 3 août 1381, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 37 ans, et a été enterrée à St Ambrose's Church, Whitehall, Bristol, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni."},"de":{"Abt 1345–3 August 1381":"um 1345–3. August 1381","1345–1381":"1345–1381","1346–1431":"1346–1431","1346–Female":"1346–Verstorben","1335–1412":"1335–1412","1362–1387":"1362–1387","1388–1445":"1388–1445","1322–1389":"1322–1389","1318–1400":"1318–1400","1362":"1362","1361":"1361","Abt 1345":"um 1345","1381":"1381","3 August 1381":"3. August 1381","1347":"1347","1445":"1445","1412":"1412","1335":"1335","1346":"1346","1400":"1400","1389":"1389","1345":"1345","1322":"1322","1388":"1388","1387":"1387","1431":"1431","1318":"1318","Hopton, Suffolk, England":"Hopton, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom","Whitehall St Ambrose, Gloucestershire, England, United Kingdom":"St Ambrose's Church, Whitehall, Bristol, England, United Kingdom","Bristol, Gloucestershire, England":"Bristol, Gloucestershire, England","Shropshire, England, United Kingdom":"Shropshire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Als Joan Yonge um 1345 in Bristol, Gloucestershire, England geboren wurde, war ihr Vater Thomas Yonge 25 und ihre Mutter Isold Hawberke 28. Sie hat 1361 in Hopton, Suffolk, England, United Kingdom Walter Hopton geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 2 Söhne. Sie starb am 3. August 1381 im Alter von 37 Jahren in ihrem Geburtsort und wurde in St Ambrose's Church, Whitehall, Bristol, England, United Kingdom begraben."},"ht":{"Abt 1345–3 August 1381":"about 1345–3 August 1381","1345–1381":"1345–1381","1346–1431":"1346–1431","1346–Female":"1346–Desede","1335–1412":"1335–1412","1362–1387":"1362–1387","1388–1445":"1388–1445","1322–1389":"1322–1389","1318–1400":"1318–1400","1362":"1362","1361":"1361","Abt 1345":"about 1345","1381":"1381","3 August 1381":"3 August 1381","1347":"1347","1